| AnalysisResult | analysis-service | Graduation eligibility evaluation output |

## Layers or Architectural Framework

Describe the layered model:

```
Browser (React) → api-gateway → {auth, rule, analysis}-service → PostgreSQL
                              → analysis-service → Kafka → parser-service
```

Frontend: feature-based React with role-protected routes.
Backend: controller → service → repository pattern in Spring Boot services.
Event layer: Kafka for async parser integration.

